Install Eclipse for Java. Create a project,then package and then class. The guidelines for installing can be found here [https://www.vogella.com/tutorials/Eclipse/article.html]

1)Code to Print something

   package first;

public class One {

	public static void main(String ar[]) {
		System.out.println("hello, i DID IT");
	}
}

2)Java code to print some of two numbers

package first;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class One {

	public static void main(String ar[]) {
		System.out.println("enter 2 number");
		Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
		int a=s.nextInt();
		int b=s.nextInt();
		int c=a+b;
				
		System.out.println("Result:"+c);
	}

}
